high_descs: Move to in between to two sinks to the right of the shower
Pick up dispenser from off of the counter
Move to the right side of the sink cabinets
Open cabinet door and place dispenser inside and close door
Move to the counter space in between the two sinks to the right of the shower
Pick up the other dispenser from up off the counter
Move to the right side of the sink cabinets
Open cabinet door and place dispenser inside next to the other one and close door
anns.task_desc: Put both dispensers on the bathroom counter into the right hand side sink cabinet.

high_descs: Turn to the right and face the cabinet with two sinks.
Pick up the white bottle of soap furthest from the front ledge.
Move in front of the sink on the right side.
Put the bottle of soap into the bottom right cabinet close to the edge and to the right of the pink bar of soap.
Move to the left in front of the second bottle of soap.
Pick up the second white bottle of soap.
Move in front of the sink on the right side.
Put the second bottle of soap behind the first bottle of soap in the lower right cabinet
anns.task_desc: Put two bottle of soap into the lower right cabinet.

high_descs: turn to face the counter between the two sinks
pick up the lotion bottle towards the back part of the counter
move to the right slightly and face the cabinet door to the right
open the cabinet door on the right, put the lotion bottle in the cabinet and close the door
move back to the center of the counter facing the other lotion bottle
pick up the lotion bottle that is on the counter
move to the right and face the cabinet door on the right
open the cabinet door, put the second bottle of lotion in to the cabinet behind the first bottle and close the cabinet door
anns.task_desc: put two bottles of lotion into the cabinet
